    <h3>Related Financial Instruments</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Buy Now Pay Later (BNPL)</strong>: Short-term installment payments, typically 3-6 months, often merchant-funded (0% interest)</li>
      <li><strong>Prepaid cards</strong>: Non-reloadable cards for online shopping without bank account requirements</li>
      <li><strong>Virtual cards</strong>: Digital-only card numbers for secure online transactions</li>
      <li><strong>Super-app wallets</strong>: Integrated payment within Grab, Zalo, Shopee ecosystems</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

